<H2>General Information about the Vienna International Centre</H2>
<HR>
<h3>
Arrival in Vienna 
</h3>
<h4>
Airport Service
</h4>
<P>
Buses from the Airport to the City Air Terminal leave every 20 minutes. 
<P>
Bus service between VIC and Airport:
<P>
<PRE>
Departure from VIC/Wagramerstrasse	Departure from Airport
<P>
Hours                                   Hours
<P>
08.40                                   07.50
09.40                                   08.50
11.40                                   10.50
13.40                                   12.50
16.40 (travel time 35 minutes)          15.50
18.50
<P>
</PRE>
With the exception of the bus at l6:40 (which goes directly to the airport),
the journey takes 50 min. and is via the City Air Terminal.
<h4>
U-Bahn (Underground)
</h4>
<P>
Tickets and passes can be bought at tobacco stores ("Tabak Trafik") and during working
hours at the News Stand in the VIC.

