<HEAD>
<TITLE>BOG Rules of Procedure</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
<H2>Provisional Rules of Procedure  of the Board of Governors</H2>
As Amended up to 23 February 1989
</CENTER>
<HR>
