<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>International Symposium on Isotope Techniques in the Study of Past and Current Environmental Changes in the Hydrosphere and the Atmosphere</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE="-1" FACE="Arial, Helvetica">
