</B>
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> General information; Introduction;
Thorium-carbon
system; Protactinium-carbon system; Uranium-carbon system;
Neptunium-carbon system; Plutonium-carbon system;
Americium-carbon system; References; Appendix: Tables of
thermodynamic functions.
