<B>
IAEA Safety Codes and Guides (NUSS) in the Light of Current
Safety Issues
<BR>
<I>Proceedings Series</I>
</B>
<P>
Proceedings of a symposium, Vienna, 29 October to 2 November
1984. This symposium was organized to discuss the dilemma between
maintaining standards unchanged during the lifetime of the plants
and changing standards to adapt plants to developments in safety
standards. Although relating specifically to the programme, it is
also relevant to the development of safety standards in general.
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> NUSS objectives and results; Conduct of
regulatory inspection and enforcement; Probabilistic safety
