for ageing management studies; 4. Methodology for ageing
management studies; 5. Recommendations for ageing management
pilot studies; Appendix I: Examples of ageing related component
degradation and failure; Appendix II: Ageing degradation
mechanisms and susceptible materials and components; Appendix
III: Examples of summary results of ageing management studies
from the USNRC's Nuclear Plant Ageing Research Programme;
Appendix IV: Examples of condition indicator trending as a basis
for mitigating component ageing.
