<B>
<A NAME=84>Establishing the Quality Assurance Programme  for a
Nuclear Power
Plant Project: A Safety Guide 
<BR>
<I>Safety Series No. 50-SG-QA1</I></A>
</B>
<P>
Requirements, recommendations and examples for establishing the
overall quality assurance programme, and its constituent
programmes, for a nuclear power plant project. It also provides
guidance on the planning and documenting of programme plans and
actions. Applicable to all organizations performing activities
affecting the quality throughout the design, procurement,
manufacture, construction, commissioning, operation and
decommissioning of a nuclear power plant.
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> Introduction; Basic principles for establishing
the quality assurance programme; Planning for implementation of
the quality assurance programme; Documenting the quality
assurance programme; Annex A: Structure and content of quality
assurance programme documentation.
<P>
STI/PUB/663 (44 pp.; 1984)
