<A NAME=85>Quality Assurance Records System for Nuclear Power
Plants: A
Safety Guide
<BR>
<I>Safety Series No. 50-SG-QA2</I></A>
</B>
<P>
Requirements and recommendations for identifying, collecting,
indexing, filing, storing, maintaining and dispositioning of the
records associated with the design, manufacture, construction,
commissioning and operation of nuclear power plants. Applicable
to the responsible organization and other organizations involved
with the supply of items and services for nuclear power plants.
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> Introduction; Establishment of a records system;
Categorization of records; Records system; Storage, preservation
and safekeeping; Inspection.
