for
underground disposal of solid radioactive wastes. It is intended
to
serve both implementing and regulatory bodies when an underground
disposal system is being developed.
<P>
<I>Contents:</I> Introduction; Scope; Underground disposal
systems;
Basic requirements; Criteria; Concluding remarks; Annex I:
Optimization for the post-operational phase of a repository for
underground disposal; References; Selected bibliography.
