<B>
Preparedness of the Operating Organization (Licensee) for
Emergencies at Nuclear Power Plants: A Safety Guide 
<BR>
<I>Safety Series No. 50-SG-O6</I>
</B>
<P>
(See under <A HREF=oper.html#47>Nuclear Power Plants, NUSS
